<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="101400000t" end="145000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">「約定的夢幻島 S2」</p>
<p begin="169400000t" end="208200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">(回想起來了　回想起來了)</p>
<p begin="209000000t" end="248200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">(在那一眨眼間的絕望感覺)</p>
<p begin="249000000t" end="288200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">(即使醒來了　仍然在夢中)</p>
<p begin="289000000t" end="331800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">(夢見我們剎那光輝的故事)</p>
<p begin="333800000t" end="373000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">(時鐘的秒針)</p>
<p begin="373800000t" end="403000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">(請對我報以微笑吧)</p>
<p begin="403800000t" end="464200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(滿腦子心心念念的都是你啊)</p>
<p begin="489400000t" end="527800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(打破冰封三尺的明日吧)</p>
<p begin="528600000t" end="568200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">(盡是些絕對不能失去的事物)</p>
<p begin="569000000t" end="608200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">(我在命運指引的前路上找到了你)</p>
<p begin="609000000t" end="647000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">(如今眼淚已再也沒有意義)</p>
<p begin="647800000t" end="687000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(在飛快地運轉的世界一角)</p>
<p begin="687800000t" end="728600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(有如吶喊一樣呼吸著)</p>
<p begin="729400000t" end="767800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(如能在跨越千千萬萬時光後重逢)</p>
<p begin="768600000t" end="810600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(就在絕望的前方一步笑吧)</p>
<p begin="989600000t" end="1018400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">來光顧吧，過來看看</p>
<p begin="1027600000t" end="1040800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">很美味的</p>
<p begin="1055600000t" end="1070800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">過來嘗嘗吧</p>
<p begin="1090800000t" end="1109200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">過來看看，挑選一下吧</p>
<p begin="1116000000t" end="1130000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">我也要</p>
<p begin="1145600000t" end="1158800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">很美味的</p>
<p begin="1208800000t" end="1227200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">過來…過來看看吧</p>
<p begin="1242000000t" end="1256000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">既美味，又便宜</p>
<p begin="1298800000t" end="1332000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">有聽過又有農場被洗劫了嗎</p>
<p begin="1332800000t" end="1368000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">想去偷食用兒童，最近越來越多</p>
<p begin="1376800000t" end="1407200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">對，我有本事也想去偷</p>
<p begin="1592000000t" end="1610400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">那些高質素的頂級肉</p>
<p begin="1611200000t" end="1637600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">全都被送到鬼貴族那裡</p>
<p begin="1638400000t" end="1663600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">真的很想品嘗高級農場的頂級肉</p>
<p begin="1664400000t" end="1681600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">一次也好</p>
<p begin="1692000000t" end="1723600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">恩典農場走失的那批貨還沒找到嗎</p>
<p begin="1733600000t" end="1759200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">這件事發生了差不多一年</p>
<p begin="1762800000t" end="1782400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">恐怕早就死光了</p>
<p begin="2302000000t" end="2326400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">(2047年1月24日)</p>
<p begin="2354800000t" end="2374000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">(草藥:艾蒿、地榆、白屈菜)</p>
<p begin="2374800000t" end="2394000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">(聖約翰草、竹節參)</p>
<p begin="2883600000t" end="2896400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">你們回來了…</p>
<p begin="2897200000t" end="2922800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">回來了，不好意思，晚了</p>
<p begin="2964400000t" end="2981200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">艾瑪，怎麼樣</p>
<p begin="3003200000t" end="3013200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">你看</p>
<p begin="3026000000t" end="3038800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">對不起</p>
<p begin="3039600000t" end="3068800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">我們今天只拿到這麼多食物回來</p>
<p begin="3071600000t" end="3095200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">不要緊　　沒問題</p>
<p begin="3286400000t" end="3298000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">歡迎回來…</p>
<p begin="3302000000t" end="3314400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">你們怎麼樣</p>
<p begin="3457200000t" end="3474400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">我不客氣了…</p>
<p begin="3502000000t" end="3537600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">這些留待明天吃，而後天卻…</p>
<p begin="3551600000t" end="3564400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="3583200000t" end="3597600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">明天我們一定</p>
<p begin="3602000000t" end="3620000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">會找到很多食物回來的</p>
<p begin="3620800000t" end="3655200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">別勉強自己，大家少分一點就行了</p>
<p begin="3656000000t" end="3674000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">只要在煮湯時加入創意</p>
<p begin="3674800000t" end="3685200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">已經截然不同了</p>
<p begin="3686000000t" end="3702800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">我最喜歡喝湯</p>
<p begin="3714000000t" end="3734800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">不過…　　沒關係，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="3738400000t" end="3767200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">我相信大家都不會介意</p>
<p begin="3886800000t" end="3908800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">(好了，結束通話吧)</p>
<p begin="3917200000t" end="3929600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">太好了</p>
<p begin="3930400000t" end="3956400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">就是說今天孤兒院沒甚麼事發生</p>
<p begin="3962400000t" end="3977200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">那我們以後怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="3986400000t" end="4020400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">總不能一輩子一直在躲藏</p>
<p begin="4030000000t" end="4054400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">幸好這裡可以避開那些追兵</p>
<p begin="4055200000t" end="4074400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">而且能接收到電波訊號</p>
<p begin="4075200000t" end="4097200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">知道孤兒院發生的情況</p>
<p begin="4109600000t" end="4130800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">自從避難所受到襲擊</p>
<p begin="4131600000t" end="4150400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">我們就一直原地踏步</p>
<p begin="4213200000t" end="4232800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">如果避難所還在就好了</p>
<p begin="4233600000t" end="4246000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">現時在這裡</p>
<p begin="4246800000t" end="4270000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">根本沒有能力接菲爾他們來</p>
<p begin="4273200000t" end="4289600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">我們也自顧不暇</p>
<p begin="4324000000t" end="4336800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">很遠</p>
<p begin="4338800000t" end="4350800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">你覺得我們</p>
<p begin="4356400000t" end="4382000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">真的有能力到達那個地方嗎</p>
<p begin="4513200000t" end="4532000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">我很討厭我自己</p>
<p begin="4545600000t" end="4566000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">我明明很清楚</p>
<p begin="4578400000t" end="4600800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">想好了才做決定的</p>
<p begin="4705200000t" end="4733200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">在外面等著我們的是鬼的世界</p>
<p begin="4734000000t" end="4759200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">想離開孤兒院在外面生活</p>
<p begin="4760000000t" end="4776800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">就等於叫大家</p>
<p begin="4777600000t" end="4803600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">在敵人包圍下生活一樣</p>
<p begin="4818000000t" end="4856400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">無論起居飲食，所有大小事情</p>
<p begin="4857200000t" end="4880000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">都要靠自己的力量找回來</p>
<p begin="4905200000t" end="4922000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">我明明很清楚</p>
<p begin="4934000000t" end="4962000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">才決定帶大家離開孤兒院</p>
<p begin="4966800000t" end="4994800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">我本來應該保護好他們才對</p>
<p begin="5004000000t" end="5024800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">但結果要他們受苦</p>
<p begin="5034800000t" end="5059600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">還要每天為生存而煩惱</p>
<p begin="5074400000t" end="5089200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">明明知道不可以委屈他們</p>
<p begin="5090000000t" end="5107600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">住在這種地方</p>
<p begin="5115200000t" end="5128400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">明明知道</p>
<p begin="5133200000t" end="5162800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">必須儘快救出菲爾他們才行</p>
<p begin="5186790000t" end="5204800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">但我甚麼都做不到</p>
<p begin="5210390000t" end="5227600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">還連累了大家</p>
<p begin="5230800000t" end="5263600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">我真的…很沒用</p>
<p begin="5264400000t" end="5279600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">我可以生存到今天</p>
<p begin="5282800000t" end="5308400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">是因為當初跟你一起逃走</p>
<p begin="5334400000t" end="5346000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">其他人也是</p>
<p begin="5349600000t" end="5364800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">我們沒有人會責怪你</p>
<p begin="5372800000t" end="5399600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">所以你也別責怪自己了</p>
<p begin="5406800000t" end="5424800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">你做的決定很正確</p>
<p begin="5429200000t" end="5447200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">我們所有人都沒有做錯決定</p>
<p begin="5454000000t" end="5476400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">專心考慮將來的事更好</p>
<p begin="5573600000t" end="5587600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">艾瑪…</p>
<p begin="5600000000t" end="5622000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">我們都想幫忙去尋找食物</p>
<p begin="5627600000t" end="5652800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">今天我們無論如何要跟你們一起去</p>
<p begin="5653600000t" end="5676000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">但途中會經過鬼村落</p>
<p begin="5676800000t" end="5694400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">你倆真的可以嗎</p>
<p begin="5695200000t" end="5707200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">當然可以</p>
<p begin="5708000000t" end="5732800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">求求你吧，我們一定會很小心</p>
<p begin="5733600000t" end="5762000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">你看，我們還特意製作了鬼面具</p>
<p begin="5762800000t" end="5782400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">而且會掩蓋氣味</p>
<p begin="5786800000t" end="5811200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">這個面具真的製作得不錯</p>
<p begin="5812000000t" end="5838800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">單看外表應該不會被發現</p>
<p begin="5874800000t" end="5900800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">你們這麼有心，我真的很開心</p>
<p begin="5946800000t" end="5976000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">還是不行，始終太危險了</p>
<p begin="5986000000t" end="6010800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">我們真的很想幫忙</p>
<p begin="6011600000t" end="6038800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">我們一定可以找到很多食物回來</p>
<p begin="6039600000t" end="6055200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">求求你吧　　你就讓他們去吧</p>
<p begin="6088400000t" end="6100800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">那好吧</p>
<p begin="6109600000t" end="6138000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">不過你們要保證一定會很小心</p>
<p begin="6138800000t" end="6170400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">絕對不可以被鬼發現我們是人類</p>
<p begin="6183200000t" end="6205200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">太好了…</p>
<p begin="6675000000t" end="6693000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">你們還沒走？</p>
<p begin="6693800000t" end="6709800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">對　　還在這裡</p>
<p begin="6712600000t" end="6741000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">你們乖乖地快點回家吧</p>
<p begin="6743800000t" end="6787400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">我說過很多次，這裡是邪血的神殿</p>
<p begin="6789800000t" end="6827000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">小孩絕對不可以單獨留在這個地方</p>
<p begin="6827800000t" end="6837000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">是</p>
<p begin="7232600000t" end="7242200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="7388200000t" end="7401800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">全都在這裡</p>
<p begin="7552600000t" end="7581000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">你的名字是艾瑪嗎</p>
<p begin="7584200000t" end="7601800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">這個名字很動聽</p>
<p begin="7635000000t" end="7651400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">很感謝你</p>
<p begin="7675400000t" end="7715400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">神明在上，真的很感謝你</p>
<p begin="7716200000t" end="7751000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">賜予我們平安和潔淨的食物</p>
<p begin="7751800000t" end="7797800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">請以後繼續保佑我和我的家人</p>
<p begin="7821000000t" end="7865400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">希望農場以後可以分更多肉給我們</p>
<p begin="7866200000t" end="7887800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">那就感激不盡了</p>
<p begin="7896200000t" end="7912600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">如果再這樣下去</p>
<p begin="7913400000t" end="7929000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">相信不用多久</p>
<p begin="7929800000t" end="7951400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">我們的村子就會陸續出現</p>
<p begin="7952200000t" end="7975400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">退化的野生鬼了</p>
<p begin="7976200000t" end="8001000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">世界始終沒有改變</p>
<p begin="8126600000t" end="8157400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">我祝福你們可以吃到好的食物</p>
<p begin="8158200000t" end="8179400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">不用為兩餐煩惱</p>
<p begin="8187800000t" end="8200200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">再見了</p>
<p begin="8284600000t" end="8294600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="8305800000t" end="8327400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">真是的，你怎麼能胡來</p>
<p begin="8328200000t" end="8345000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">被他識穿了怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="8347800000t" end="8369400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">對不起，我太衝動了</p>
<p begin="8370200000t" end="8392600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">不過感覺真的很奇怪</p>
<p begin="8396600000t" end="8412600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">自從由孤兒院出來</p>
<p begin="8413400000t" end="8421000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">為了避開鬼</p>
<p begin="8421800000t" end="8443800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">我們無時無刻都會提高警覺</p>
<p begin="8444600000t" end="8481400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">想不到現在竟然會近距離跟鬼說話</p>
<p begin="8489800000t" end="8503800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">而且這半年來</p>
<p begin="8504600000t" end="8531000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">我們一直在這裡生活得相安無事</p>
<p begin="8533800000t" end="8554200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">別忘記那個老伯伯是鬼</p>
<p begin="8555000000t" end="8574200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">他也是靠吃人為生的</p>
<p begin="8581000000t" end="8599400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">如果被他發現我們是人類</p>
<p begin="8600200000t" end="8614600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">那就糟糕了</p>
<p begin="8619000000t" end="8636600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">不過他拿來了一些祭品</p>
<p begin="8637400000t" end="8653400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">也算幫得上忙</p>
<p begin="8654200000t" end="8672200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">原來鬼除了吃人之外</p>
<p begin="8673000000t" end="8690200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">還會吃其他東西</p>
<p begin="8695000000t" end="8703000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">如果所有鬼</p>
<p begin="8703800000t" end="8734600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">都像孫居和穆吉卡那樣不吃人</p>
<p begin="8735400000t" end="8749400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">你說該有多好</p>
<p begin="8760200000t" end="8770200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">家人</p>
<p begin="8777000000t" end="8787400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">剛才那位老伯伯</p>
<p begin="8788200000t" end="8810600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">是為了他的家人祈禱的</p>
<p begin="8818600000t" end="8841400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">想不到鬼也有家人</p>
<p begin="8866600000t" end="8876600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">哥哥</p>
<p begin="8877400000t" end="8908600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">對不起，我今天買不到任何東西</p>
<p begin="8918600000t" end="8935400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">沒事，沒關係</p>
<p begin="8936200000t" end="8957400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">對，我們沒事</p>
<p begin="8996200000t" end="9009800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">要快點想辦法</p>
<p begin="9010600000t" end="9037000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">找一些像樣的肉回來給他們吃才行</p>
<p begin="9037800000t" end="9062200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">昨天說的那件事　　哪件事</p>
<p begin="9063000000t" end="9088200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">在恩典農場逃走了的那批頂級肉</p>
<p begin="9089000000t" end="9102200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">不是還沒找到嗎</p>
<p begin="9103000000t" end="9121400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">不是吧？你又提起這件事？</p>
<p begin="9122200000t" end="9143400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">這麼久也找不到，就是已經死去了</p>
<p begin="9144200000t" end="9175000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">但我聽說農場還一直四處尋找</p>
<p begin="9175800000t" end="9205400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">最近還增加了人手和提高懸賞金</p>
<p begin="9206200000t" end="9235400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">而且搜索範圍就在附近一帶</p>
<p begin="9236200000t" end="9248600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">你說就在這附近？</p>
<p begin="9249400000t" end="9268600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">對，就是說頂級品</p>
<p begin="9269400000t" end="9289400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">很有可能就在附近</p>
<p begin="9290200000t" end="9305800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">別那麼天真</p>
<p begin="9319800000t" end="9349400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">但如果這是真的…</p>
<p begin="9354200000t" end="9382600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">懸賞金有多少對我們並不重要</p>
<p begin="9383400000t" end="9408200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">只要得到恩典農場的肉</p>
<p begin="9412600000t" end="9439800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">只要讓他們吃到恩典農場的肉</p>
<p begin="9442600000t" end="9454600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">那麼他們…</p>
<p begin="9459400000t" end="9480600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">那麼他們的退化…</p>
<p begin="9483000000t" end="9499000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">就會停止</p>
<p begin="9515400000t" end="9528600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">快點去尋找吧</p>
<p begin="9529400000t" end="9557000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">找到那些肉，他們就有救了　　好</p>
<p begin="9571800000t" end="9584200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">我來了，托馬</p>
<p begin="9585000000t" end="9603000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">儘管來吧，拉尼恩</p>
<p begin="9631000000t" end="9654200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">好吧，看你能跑到哪裡去</p>
<p begin="9684600000t" end="9703800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">你們看，這麼快就捉到一條了</p>
<p begin="9704600000t" end="9729800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">我們這個捉魚的方法很厲害吧</p>
<p begin="9730600000t" end="9748600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">對，真的很厲害</p>
<p begin="9749400000t" end="9778600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">看來今晚大家可以飽餐一頓了</p>
<p begin="9779400000t" end="9791800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">來吧　　接住</p>
<p begin="9792600000t" end="9809000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">繼續　　快點吧</p>
<p begin="9809800000t" end="9823400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">太好了</p>
<p begin="9833400000t" end="9856600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">這個份量應該足夠今晚吃</p>
<p begin="9857400000t" end="9875400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">只是剛好足夠今晚吃而已</p>
<p begin="9876200000t" end="9901800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">對吧？到時艾瑪他們又會假裝吃了</p>
<p begin="9902600000t" end="9935000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">對，他們經常不吃，全都讓我們吃</p>
<p begin="9935800000t" end="9953800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">要想想辦法才行</p>
<p begin="9977400000t" end="9987000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">讓我看看</p>
<p begin="9987800000t" end="10008200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">這裡應該足夠大家今晚吃了</p>
<p begin="10009000000t" end="10020600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">但我突然很想吃</p>
<p begin="10021400000t" end="10052600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">艾瑪從市集拿回來的乾果</p>
<p begin="10053400000t" end="10075400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">對，反正路經市集</p>
<p begin="10076200000t" end="10113400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">順便買一些調味料回去吧　　好</p>
<p begin="10139800000t" end="10174200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">很熱鬧　　這裡就是鬼市集嗎</p>
<p begin="10193400000t" end="10203000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">來看看吧</p>
<p begin="10203800000t" end="10231400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">過來看看吧，又便宜又新鮮又划算</p>
<p begin="10237000000t" end="10253800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">好像很吸引</p>
<p begin="10254600000t" end="10271400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">你們跟緊一點</p>
<p begin="10313000000t" end="10329800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">托馬，看看那邊</p>
<p begin="10395790000t" end="10414200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">對不起，沒事吧</p>
<p begin="10441800000t" end="10455000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">起來吧，小孩</p>
<p begin="10459400000t" end="10471400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">怎麼回事</p>
<p begin="10508600000t" end="10532200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">為何好像有一股食物的香味</p>
<p begin="10543400000t" end="10557400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">我也嗅到</p>
<p begin="10571400000t" end="10593000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">是從這個袋子裡傳出來的嗎</p>
<p begin="10615000000t" end="10634600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">原來不是人肉嗎</p>
<p begin="10640200000t" end="10651400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">謝謝你</p>
<p begin="10660200000t" end="10669000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">真的很危險</p>
<p begin="10669800000t" end="10696200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">慢著，我真的嗅到</p>
<p begin="10697000000t" end="10714600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">是人類的氣味</p>
<p begin="10892600000t" end="10912600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">對不起　　我們只是…</p>
<p begin="10915800000t" end="10946200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">沒關係，只有那兩隻鬼發現而已</p>
<p begin="10950600000t" end="10971400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">你打算如何回去秘密基地</p>
<p begin="10972200000t" end="10986200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">現在不可以回去</p>
<p begin="10987000000t" end="11000200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">萬一途中被他們發現</p>
<p begin="11001000000t" end="11015800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">就會連累大家</p>
<p begin="11016600000t" end="11034200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">對，說得對</p>
<p begin="11042600000t" end="11057800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">那我和艾瑪去引開他們</p>
<p begin="11061800000t" end="11073800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">你們就趁機離開這裡</p>
<p begin="11074600000t" end="11092200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">然後繞路走，先回去基地吧</p>
<p begin="11102600000t" end="11116200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">唐、吉爾妲，拜託你們</p>
<p begin="11117000000t" end="11136200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">交給我們吧…　　不過…</p>
<p begin="11149000000t" end="11159400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">快跑吧</p>
<p begin="11208200000t" end="11224600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">你去那邊包抄他們</p>
<p begin="11421400000t" end="11432200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">你去追那個</p>
<p begin="12132600000t" end="12142600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">在這邊</p>
<p begin="12161000000t" end="12173800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">擺脫了他們</p>
<p begin="12174600000t" end="12195400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">我們要找一個地方暫時躲起來</p>
<p begin="12391800000t" end="12400600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">在這裡</p>
<p begin="12401400000t" end="12426600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">快滾，是我們先發現獵物的</p>
<p begin="12427400000t" end="12444200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">你休想來搶</p>
<p begin="12609000000t" end="12619000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="12680200000t" end="12692600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">不會的</p>
<p begin="12757400000t" end="12769400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">諾曼…</p>
<p begin="12779800000t" end="12795800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">終於都見面了</p>
<p begin="12841400000t" end="12867800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">(當你許下願望)</p>
<p begin="12868600000t" end="12895000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">(月亮就灑下了影子)</p>
<p begin="12895800000t" end="12951800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">(像魔法一般的夜晚必定融化無蹤)</p>
<p begin="13059800000t" end="13086200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">(以澄澈響亮的聲音)</p>
<p begin="13087000000t" end="13113400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">(風宣布了夜色來臨)</p>
<p begin="13114200000t" end="13140600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">(藍色世界的一切)</p>
<p begin="13141400000t" end="13168200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">(都在童話裡沉睡)</p>
<p begin="13169000000t" end="13195000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">(你在半夢半醒之間)</p>
<p begin="13195800000t" end="13221800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">(張開了閉著的眼瞼)</p>
<p begin="13222600000t" end="13247000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">(比我心裡所想的)</p>
<p begin="13247800000t" end="13283400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">(還要更加朦朧)</p>
<p begin="13299800000t" end="13348200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">(如果這聲音能傳達)</p>
<p begin="13349000000t" end="13375000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">(即使得不到回應　也想在你身旁)</p>
<p begin="13375800000t" end="13407400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">(不想讓這個故事畫下句點)</p>
<p begin="13408200000t" end="13457000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">(跨越長夜而去吧)</p>
<p begin="13457800000t" end="13483000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">(跟你在一起　就再也不需要言語)</p>
<p begin="13483800000t" end="13530200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">(如今只想確認彼此的溫度)</p>
<p begin="13531000000t" end="13566200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">(讓我沉入不會醒的美夢吧)</p>
<p begin="13567000000t" end="13613000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">(我們緊握著那雙手)</p>
<p begin="13613800000t" end="13642600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">(靜靜地祈願著)</p>
